name: In the middle of nowhere 1
description:
In the middle of Bismark Sea, Papua New Guinea coast. On the way from Lihir Island to Madang. It was a Sunday  evening after hard week at port. After dinner I came on deck and I was very impressed with the view that opened all around of me.
So beautiful sunsets I saw only at sea. It's the most powerful inspiration for me. What about you?
Decision to become a seaman I took very suddenly. I grew in small miners city 40 km from Donets. At the last year of school Donbass war began and I had no choices to stay there more. I chose nautical academy in Odessa and it was best decision in my life.
No any postproduction made on this picture.
